Package com.vsta.model

Class Vessel

java.lang.Object
com.vsta.model.Vessel
@Entity
public class Vessel
extends java.lang.Object
Represents a Voyage on the real-time information about vessel berthing times, retrieved from the retrieveByBerthingDate API provided by PORTNET.

    • getStatus

      public java.lang.String getStatus()
      Gets the Status of this Voyage object.
      Returns:
      This Voyage's Status.

      The possible values are:
      - BERTHING which means Voyage is on the way to the berth
      - ALONGSIDE which means Voyage is at the berth
      - UNBERTHED which means Voyage left the berth
